  <brief_title>Home-Based Versus Partner-Friendly Clinic Testing to Enhance Male Partner HIV-1 Testing During Pregnancy</brief_title>
  <official_title>Home-Based Versus Partner-Friendly Clinic Testing to Enhance Male Partner HIV-1 Testing During Pregnancy: A Randomized Clinical Trial</official_title>
  <sponsors>
